      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (Lab A: n=6, Lab B: n=5). All specimens from production lots; CMM dimensional inspection confirmed all screws and rods within drawing tolerances. Inter-laboratory variability in stiffness <4% (CV). Required Gradation 3 achieved."
