      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA input parameters (geometry, material, boundary conditions) demonstrably matched to test specimen measurements.",
      "rationale": "FEA model geometry updated per CMM measurements of each test specimen lot. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry (45° angled UHMWPE blocks, fixed base, actuator displacement at superior block). Material properties matched to coupon test results. Correspondence table mapping each FEA input to its experimental measurement source provided in technical report. Required Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
