      "rationale": "Three QoIs compared: construct stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement. E/uval values: 0.41 (stiffness), 0.88 (yield force), 0.29 (force at 40 mm). Percent differences: 1.3%, 2.3%, 0.7% respectively. All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria. Required Gradation 3 achieved."
